text: Myechyslaw Ivanavich Hryb (, , , born on 25 September 1938) was the eleventh Chairman of the Supreme Soviet of Belarus from 28 January 1994 to 10 January 1996. Hryb created the first Constitution of Belarus. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Belarus
title: Myechyslaw Hryb
